  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Step into the Unknown</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to STAaRS, a unique investigative simulation where you take on the role of a volunteer tasked with uncovering unknown activities. In STAaRS, you will navigate a 24-hour test where strange events appear randomly in a virtual house. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Investigate and Report</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When an activity is detected, you'll enter the virtual house through a portal to investigate. Your mission is to observe, categorize, and report these activities, which are divided into four key areas: Space, Time, Anomalies, and Reality.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/6b5918bcb24fe4e312c19dcae6a9a0e7.poster.avif?t=1744390228\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/6b5918bcb24fe4e312c19dcae6a9a0e7.webm?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/6b5918bcb24fe4e312c19dcae6a9a0e7.mp4?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Test Your Skills</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This simulation challenges your observational abilities and decision-making under pressure, preparing you for real-world scenarios.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/775aba20cb8c9fd0a0140f45c9e3e9ed.poster.avif?t=1744390228\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/775aba20cb8c9fd0a0140f45c9e3e9ed.webm?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/775aba20cb8c9fd0a0140f45c9e3e9ed.mp4?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/eb4978e97bab465419af0b9c42cd409d.poster.avif?t=1744390228\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/eb4978e97bab465419af0b9c42cd409d.webm?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/eb4978e97bab465419af0b9c42cd409d.mp4?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >22 unique mysterious activities to investigate and uncover.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic 24-hour test with random event occurrences (each test up to 25-30 real-time minutes).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interactive portal-based investigation system.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Detailed categorization and reporting mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive environment designed to test your skills.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >STAaRS offers a challenging and immersive experience where every decision matters. Are you ready to face the unknown?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Step into the Unknown</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to STAaRS, a unique investigative simulation where you take on the role of a volunteer tasked with uncovering unknown activities. In STAaRS, you will navigate a 24-hour test where strange events appear randomly in a virtual house. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Investigate and Report</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When an activity is detected, you'll enter the virtual house through a portal to investigate. Your mission is to observe, categorize, and report these activities, which are divided into four key areas: Space, Time, Anomalies, and Reality.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/6b5918bcb24fe4e312c19dcae6a9a0e7.poster.avif?t=1744390228\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/6b5918bcb24fe4e312c19dcae6a9a0e7.webm?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/6b5918bcb24fe4e312c19dcae6a9a0e7.mp4?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Test Your Skills</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This simulation challenges your observational abilities and decision-making under pressure, preparing you for real-world scenarios.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/775aba20cb8c9fd0a0140f45c9e3e9ed.poster.avif?t=1744390228\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/775aba20cb8c9fd0a0140f45c9e3e9ed.webm?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/775aba20cb8c9fd0a0140f45c9e3e9ed.mp4?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/eb4978e97bab465419af0b9c42cd409d.poster.avif?t=1744390228\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/eb4978e97bab465419af0b9c42cd409d.webm?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186340/extras/eb4978e97bab465419af0b9c42cd409d.mp4?t=1744390228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >22 unique mysterious activities to investigate and uncover.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic 24-hour test with random event occurrences (each test up to 25-30 real-time minutes).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interactive portal-based investigation system.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Detailed categorization and reporting mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive environment designed to test your skills.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >STAaRS offers a challenging and immersive experience where every decision matters. Are you ready to face the unknown?</p>",
